v class="t m0 x9 h4 y42 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls13 ws0">亲让他出家。出了家以后，他在六祖面前依止<span class="_ _b"> </span>11<span class="_ _b"> </span>年，最终</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y43 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">明心见性，成为六祖门下“一花开五叶”的五大宗匠</div><div class="t m0 x20 he y44 ffc fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1</div><div class="t m0 x21 h4 y43 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">之一。<span class="_ _9"></span> </div><div class="t m0 x1f h4 y45 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">之后，<span class="_ _6"></span>他来到南阳白崖山，<span class="_ _6"></span>在那里修行四十多年，<span class="_ _6"></span>道誉</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y46 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">甚高。<span class="_ _6"></span>唐玄宗在位时，<span class="_ _6"></span>迎请他往京城长安应供。<span class="_ _6"></span>后来发生了</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y47 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls12 ws0">“安史之乱”<span class="_ _8"></span><span class="ls14">，慧忠禅师离开长安，隐遁<span class="ls15">山林。随后，唐肃</span></span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y48 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">宗又迎请他到长安，封为国师。 </div><div class="t m0 x9 h6 y49 ff7 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">                                        <span class="_ _2"></span>               <span class="_ _5"></span> </div><div class="t m0 x9 hf y4a ff7 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1</div><div class="t m0 x22 h10 y4b ffd fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> 五大宗匠：慧忠、行思、怀让、神会、玄觉。<span class="ff7"> </span></div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
